        <i data-lucide="printer" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Document Generation Engine (iText)
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Generate Application Letter</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-normal">Create a dynamic, branded PDF application letter using MTB standards.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-4 border-t pt-6">
                    <div class="space-y-1.5">
                        <label class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Customer Name for PDF</label>
                        <input type="text" id="pdfCustName" class="flex h-10 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm focus:bg-white outline-none font-bold" value="Md. Jahidur Rahman" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-1.5">
                        <label class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">Proposed Amount (BDT)</label>
